  array (
    'name' => 'csv_grid_mapper_v2',
    'description' => 'FIXED VERSION: Parse CSV data and map rows/cells onto a text_coordinate_grid for visual rendering. Each cell becomes a token placed at (col, row) coordinates. Can optionally use a specific column as the token value or place column headers as row labels. Works with csv_table output and feeds into coordinate_grid_renderer + emoji_art_renderer pipeline. FIX: token now passed as 9th param to text_coordinate_grid.',
